        "description": "<p>About us</p>\n<p>Hubble_s is a global start-up that helps companies be better at transforming themselves by leveraging behavioral sciences through technology. We offer our clients a wide range of transformation solutions delivered through a combination of Intellectual Property &amp; Data, technology and integration services.</p>\n<p>Your role</p>\n<p>We are currently looking for a bright and high-energy level developer to join our agile and small but fast-growing team. The ideal candidate is an experienced, flexible and ambitious full stack developer who can deliver scalable software solutions and manage all the phases of the product development cycle from specification writing to testing. The primary focus of the new hire will be to build our digital platform, from where clients manage and execute their business transformations. Nonetheless, we also expect the candidate to help us envision and bring to life our many novel ideas of digital products in the coming months.</p>\n<p>At Hubble_s, you will have the opportunity to influence our strategy and drive impact from your first day! As a member of our diverse team, you can take advantage of a wide range of personal growth and learning opportunities. At Hubble_s we are committed to helping our team members achieve their life goals and priorities. To ensure this, we have established that commitment as one of our nine company principles that guide the way we interact with each other and with our clients.</p>\n<p>Our interview and onboarding process can be fully remote and everyone in our team can work from home.</p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>5 years of experience as a developer, with substantial experience in back end coding</p>\n",
