        "description": "<p>StreamUnlimited develops software and electronics for <strong>audio streaming, voice assistant devices, wireless smart speakers</strong> and is the global leader in this field. Our solutions are used by Premium Audio Brands, as well as manufacturers of Smart Home products.\nStreamUnlimited is a main player in the field of <strong>Chrome Cast built-in, Google Voice Assistant</strong> and <strong>Amazon Alexa</strong>. Headquartered in Vienna/Austria we operate offices in Bratislava, Shenzhen and Silicon Valley.</p>\n<p>For the offices in Bratislava, Iasi and Vienna we are looking for an:</p>\n<p><strong>Embedded Software Developer C/C++</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Your responsibilites</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>You develop new software solutions based on our streaming platforms. The scope of work ranges from Internet Services (i.e. Spotify), through Audio Engines (GStreamer) to GUI (QT)</li>\n<li>You create concepts, implement them and validate new functions and features</li>\n<li>Beside working on customer-projects you are involved in internal research projects (Multiroom systems, IoT)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Your profile</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Programming in C/C++ on Linux platform</li>\n<li>Object oriented programming</li>\n<li>You are familiar with network and internet standards</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>You have a great opportunity to apply your knowledge if you have some experience in one or more of the following fields</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Knowledge of Linux components GStreamer, Boost or DBus</li>\n<li>Linux kernel drivers</li>\n<li>Open Embedded/Yocto build system</li>\n<li>U-boot</li>\n<li>XML/json based interfaces</li>\n<li>Knowledge of Board Support Package software layer (e.g. for NXP i.MX8, i.MX8, or others)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What we offer</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Open vacancies in Bratislava, Iasi and Vienna</li>\n<li>Growing company with various career opportunities</li>\n<li>Team oriented and informal work environment</li>\n<li>Challenging projects</li>\n<li>Collaboration with the world's leading technology companies</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Are you interested? Please send your CV to <a href=\"mailto:career@streamunlimited.com\">career@streamunlimited.com</a> or visit us on <a href=\"https://www.streamunlimited.com/career/\">our career page</a></p>\n",
